40/thread", "/user/198"], "image_list": ["http://i.imgur.com/EWo49Pd.jpg"], "html": "<div author=\"@genji\" class=\"quote\" source=\"/post/67040/thread\" timestamp=\"1495141751\"><div class=\"quote_body\"><div class=\"quote_avatar_container\"><div class=\"avatar-wrapper avatar_size_quote avatar-198\" title=\"Lord Genji\"><img alt=\"Lord Genji Avatar\" src=\"http://i.imgur.com/EWo49Pd.jpg\"/></div></div><div class=\"quote_header\"><a href=\"/post/67040/thread\"><abbr class=\"o-timestamp time\" data-timestamp=\"1495141751000\" title=\"May 18, 2017 13:09:11 GMT -8\">May 18, 2017 13:09:11 GMT -8</abbr></a> <span itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"><a class=\"user-link js-user-link user-198 group-0\" href=\"/user/198\" itemprop=\"url\" title=\"@genji\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Lord Genji</span></a></span> said:</div><span>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0</span>Genji strode out into the courtyard. Here, a number of people had arrived and many others were out and about. It was going to be a busy day!<br><span>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0</span>He stepped down the stairs and into the morning sun, the gentle spring breeze making for a very relaxing and optimistic atmosphere. He strode over to where they all stood... Kojuro, Nakatani, Omura, Nameless Samurai, Tika, Pana, and Kiara. Judging by Omura's presence, he could extrapolate what the visitors were here for. Soon, he expected the arrival of another one of his closest retainers as well. Recent bandit activity had caused for a stir in activity.<br/><br/><i><span>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0</span>\"Good morning, everybody. Good to see you're practicing, Kojuro.. I might want to take a look at that technique later. And it's nice to see that you are back, Omura. I trust these are the ones I was looking for? Now... Which one of you is Tika?\"</i><div class=\"quote_clear\"></div></br></div></div>"}, "post-67116": {"user": null, "user_num": null, "timestamp": "1495157090000", "message": "Pana, standing next to Tika, bowed as we